QuestData.Title: Antoran High Command
QuestData.Description: The Legion has spent over 10,000 years planning their invasion of Azeroth. Defeat their leaders so they can never threaten our world again.
QuestData.LogDescription: Defeat the Antoran High Command in Antorus, the Burning Throne.

Objectives.Objective: Defeat the Antoran High Command in Antorus, The Burning Throne
